Package: pvwattsOlmoSkoplaki
Title: PV Power Forecasting Pipeline using Olmo, Skoplaki, and PVWatts Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("StÃ©fan", "Janse van Rensburg", , "stefanj@mandela.ac.za", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0749-2277"))
Description: Implements a solar PV power forecasting pipeline with Olmo transposition, Skoplaki cell temperature (two variants), PVWatts DC output, and simple AC inverter clipping. Defaults based on Trina TSM-PC05 module and De Aar site. Incorporates solar position calculation functions from the insol package by Javier G. Corripio.
